Queens: The Virgin and the Martyr (In Spanish: ) is a Spanish and British historical drama television series created by José Luis Moreno, and produced by Televisión Española with a Spanish and British cast. Production of the series had many irregularities, such as the producer falsely claiming it was coproduced by BBC.
